Accelerators for Composable Enterprise Solutions refer to pre-built frameworks or tools that speed up the creation of flexible, modular enterprise architectures. These solutions enable companies to mix and match best-of-breed services and technologies to fit their specific needs, improving scalability and agility.

See our new Product Listing

Small Update DefinedLogics' first ACES build using Next.js and Contentful leverages React Server Components for faster, more efficient content delivery. This prebuilt theme integrates smoothly with Contentful, making it easy to manage content while optimizing performance by loading data on the server. The result is a faster, more interactive experience with minimal client-side work, all while maintaining flexibility for future customization.

A flexible, open SaaS eCommerce platform that integrates seamlessly with other MACH technologies. BigCommerce supports headless architecture, allowing enterprises to deliver unique shopping experiences while leveraging its powerful, API-driven commerce engine.

Goose is a project that combines the power of Next.js, Contentful, and BigCommerce to deliver a seamless, high-performance eCommerce experience. Using Next.js for fast server-side rendering and React Server Components, Goose ensures efficient content loading and smooth user interactions. Contentful serves as the flexible CMS for managing content, while BigCommerce provides the robust backend for handling product data and transactions. Together, they create a scalable and customizable platform designed for modern eCommerce needs.
